Package io.micronaut.gcp.pubsub.validation

Annotation Interface ValidPushMessage

@Constraint(validatedBy=PushMessageValidator.class) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE) public @interface ValidPushMessage
A class-level validation constraint for PubSub push messages.
